WEBVTT

00:09:59.138 --> 00:10:02.934
being OK with sometimes not being OK.

00:10:05.468 --> 00:10:09.099
Everyone has their own
loneliness story to tell.

00:10:09.123 --> 00:10:12.794
This realization changed
everything for me.

00:10:13.910 --> 00:10:16.053
Being much more open with my emotions

00:10:16.077 --> 00:10:19.842
and concentrating much more
on my private life,

00:10:19.866 --> 00:10:22.270
my friends, my family.

00:10:23.274 --> 00:10:24.641
When we released the game,

00:10:24.665 --> 00:10:27.985
literally thousands of fans wrote us,

00:10:28.009 --> 00:10:30.606
all sharing their stories with us